UK_W02_01.Description: It was the first successful test of the pressure-based spear.​ From that moment, the number of disemboweled victims quickly trailed off.​

UK_Body006.Description: He suffered through convalescence to make a bold come back.

UK_W006.Description: First day back on the job and he was capturing the leader of the notorious Mason Kelly Gang. While the act immediately gained him recognition as a top bounty hunter, it also put him in the crosshairs of vengeful outlaws.

UK_Head007.Description: The dusty hat that bears the markings of the fight that almost killed him.

UK_Body007.Description: The skirmishes became a regular danger to citizens as collateral damage added up.

UK_W007.Description: The more people died, the more he thirsted for blood. His need for revenge was his food, faith, and fire. Nothing outside of it existed.

UK_Head01_04.Description: He used his ingenuity to find how to bring in outlaws—not dead, but alive.

UK_Body01_04.Description: He went to his workshop and immersed himself in his work to take on this new job.

UK_W01_04.Description: When he emerged, he carried the prototype of a pressure-based spear gun.

UK_Head01_4A.Description: A crown emanating a festive and ominous aura created by The Entity’s biggest fan.

UK_Head008.Description: A brilliant red hood adorned with the mighty horns of the ox.

UK_Body008.Description: An exotic robe that was wholly unfamiliar to the world Caleb had grown up in. Decorated with unusual gold markings.

UK_W008.Description: Caleb draped shreds of the red cloth on his speargun, allowing it to serve as a warning flag to those who crossed him.

UK_Head02_02.Description: Using a snowstorm as cover, he ambushed his mark and clamped him in a metal spear.

UK_Body02_02.Description: Though the man was seriously injured, he was alive and ready for incarceration.

UK_Body009.Description: He wore thick overalls, equipped with a utility belt with fresh catches and sharp hooks. As he scouted the harbor, he found his elusive bounty unloading a crate of giant squids.

UK_W009.Description: He shot his barnacle-crusted harpoon into his bounty's shoulder blade. The bounty would not get away this time.

TC_Torso012.Description: Stretched skin stitched from the shreds of his victims.

TC_Torso01_02.Description: What’s left of the tank top you wanted.

TC_W007.Description: You can find anything you need in the woods, even a sturdy weapon, such as this. Trees harbor a lot of anger, and you can help to let it out.

TC_W008.Description: Not everyone has the time to craft a club from wood, and that car's just sitting on those blocks…

TC_W01_01.Description: A hefty cattle hammer with a festive rodent flair.

TC_W01_03.Description: The hammer is remarkably clean despite the amount of blood and brains it has spilled.

TC_W04_02.Description: This weighted pickaxe was once used for chipping away at stone. These days it is used for chipping away at bone.

TC_W05_03.Description: Any frustration over the gun's damaged barrel can be alleviated by bludgeoning the stock into a victim's head.

MK_Mask01.Description: A sacred crown worn to hide the affliction that slowly overcame the freshly ordained priestess.

MK_Body01.Description: Woven from the best silks of Babylon, this robe was crafted especially for the priestess to display her new social status.

MK_W01.Description: Exuding the sweet fragrances of the gardens that the priestess used to tend to.

MK_Mask01_P01.Description: A crown drenched in blood, worn to hide the affliction that slowly overcame the freshly ordained priestess.

MK_Body01_P01.Description: Woven from the best silks of Babylon, this robe was stained with the guts of the vultures that she eviscerated.

MK_W01_P01.Description: Exuding the stench of congealed organs preserved by the priestess.

MS_Head01.Description: A no-nonsense hairstyle, perfect for more serious topics of conversation, matched with soft, friendly make-up.

MS_Torso01.Description: A stylish jacket, cut as a long bolero, matched with a crisp white dress shirt. It's time for work!

MS_Legs01.Description: Chat shows can seem like they're all about sitting, but they can be surprisingly active. Well-fitted pants are a must.

MS_Torso01_01.Description: A more casual design, for days when celebrity guests came onto the show.

MS_Head01_P01.Description: As long as it's not your blood, you can keep filming. The show must go on.

MS_Torso01_P01.Description: A stylish jacket, cut in a long bolero style, matched with what used to be a crisp white dress shirt. It's time for laundry!

MS_Legs01_P01.Description: Don't worry, our wardrobe department can get any stain out of any fabric.

OK_Mask01.Description: Just a simple plastic mask. Anyone could be behind it, using its anonymity to kill for their own reasons.

OK_Body01.Description: For the killer that needs concealment but craves attention. Black fabrics help give cover, while glossy textures provide fashionable accents.

OK_W01.Description: See how the streetlights glint on the razor-sharp edge? Anyone should feel honored to feel it sliding through their ribcage.

OK_Mask01_P01.Description: Just a simple plastic mask, though its expression seems different when blood-spattered.

OK_Body01_P01.Description: The long jacket helps to keep the rest of the clothes dry as blood splashes with each stab of the knife.

OK_W01_P01.Description: Even with the blade drenched in blood, the guard keeps the handle dry.

OK_Body01_01.Description: Black for the night, white for the traditional shroud of death.

OK_W01_01.Description: The colored handle may not affect the blade, but it certainly looks sharper.

QK_Body01.Description: An adult Demogorgon. It emerged through a rift and now wreaks terror in Hawkins, Indiana.

QK_Head01.Description: A face that blooms into five thick, fleshy strips to reveal a gaping mouth with needle-like teeth. How such a beast evolved is unknown.

QK_W01.Description: A gargantuan hand of immense strength. Its long fingers can brutalize prey.

QF_Head01.Description: A small town style worn during the school year.

QF_Torso01.Description: A warm, long-sleeved top worn during the winter of 1983

QF_Legs01.Description: A smart look to fly under the radar of high school scrutiny.

QK_Head01_P01.Description: Blood and gore drips from the stretched jaws of The Demogorgon. What became of its victim is better left unsaid.

QK_Body01_P01.Description: Is that deer blood or human blood? Probably both.

QK_W01_P01.Description: Blood trickles along the slick creases of The Demogorgon’s hand. The Hawkins Police may have another missing persons case on their hands.

QF_Head01_P01.Description: She can still take the shot if she wipes the blood from her eyes.

QF_Torso01_P01.Description: Now maybe they’ll take Barb’s disappearance seriously.

QF_Legs01_P01.Description: If it’s not your blood, whose blood is it?

QM_Head01.Description: Classic 80's feathered mullet to attract all the attention! A style for those who feel bold and confident.

QM_Torso01.Description: A relaxed look that Steve's worn through the halls of Hawkins High School.

QM_Legs01.Description: Worn on the first day of class and still holding up strong.

QM_Head01_P01.Description: If you do four puffs of hairspray no one will notice the blood splatter.

QM_Torso01_P01.Description: To be a damn good babysitter, you’ve got to be willing to face off against the boogeyman!

QM_Legs01_P01.Description: You’ve been through a lot but you’re still standing. Not bad for a kid from small town, Indiana.

QM_Torso01_01.Description: A relaxed look that Steve wore in the halls of Hawkins High School.

QF_Torso01_01.Description: Crawling into the Upside Down has its ups and downs… like ripping your favorite sweater. Thankfully, you’ll live.

GS_Torso03_SummerEvent2018_01.Description: A sleek bandana top with a free spirit print. There’s too many places to see to stay in one place. Break free, songbird!

TCW06_SummerEvent2018_01.Description: This spiked hammer combines rusty BBQ tools from the old Coldwind farmhouse. It offers a crafty way to tenderize even the most venous meat. Waste not, want not.

SwedenKiller_Head01.Description: The cruel, disciplined warrior who strove to bring purity to the samurai by exterminating the imposter samurai within its ranks.

SwedenKiller_Body01.Description: The fabric that protected his flesh and inflamed his ego.

SwedenKiller_Weapon01.Description: A long blade that was passed down from one generation to the next.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01.Description: The stubborn and daring moto racer who left home to start anew.

SwedenSurvivor_Torso01.Description: Her gang jacket with the Sakura 7 logo on the back showcasing her racing team.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs01.Description: Comfortable synthetic pants that keep the legs warm during winter. Ideal to brave the cold streets of her hometown: Hida.

SwedenKiller_Head01_P01.Description: The cruel, disciplined warrior who strove to bring purity to the samurai by exterminating the imposter samurai within its ranks… and feeding them to dogs.

SwedenKiller_Body01_P01.Description: The bloodstained fabric that protected his flesh and inflamed his ego.

SwedenKiller_W01_P01.Description: A blood-encrusted blade that shed the blood of many unfortunate souls.

SwedenSurvivor_Head01_P01.Description: The stubborn and daring moto racer who left everything to start anew and the blood she shed to defy the odds.

SwedenSurvivor_Torso01_P01.Description: Her blood-stained, gang jacket with the Sakura 7 logo on the back.

SwedenSurvivor_Legs01_P01.Description: Comfortable synthetic pants slick with blood. Ideal to brave the cold streets of her hometown: Hida.

SwedenSurvivor_Torso01_01.Description: Nothing would hold her back, not even her father's ultimatum. Her team jacket serves as a reminder of the sacrifices she made to get where she is today.

UkraineKiller_Body01.Description: A fitted, long-sleeved coat to keep his weapons and devices concealed but easy to reach.

UkraineKiller_W01.Description: A sharp weapon with a strong bite.

UK_Head01_P01.Description: An inventive and volatile engineer, Caleb derived all his passion from his groundbreaking designs. When a wealthy man stole his life's work, he sought to tear his body apart limb from limb.

UK_Body01_P01.Description: A fitted, long-sleeved coat to keep his targets from drenching his weapons and devices in blood.

UK_W01_P01.Description: A sharp weapon with a strong bite... and a thirst for blood.

US_Head01.Description: A daring, modern, workaholic filmmaker, Zarina strove to reveal hidden truths.

US_Torso01.Description: A loose jacket to conceal the recording devices she brings for improvised recordings and interviews.

US_Legs01.Description: Flexible denim pants to venture the streets of Brooklyn and brave any type of weather.

US_Head01_P01.Description: A daring, modern, workaholic filmmaker, Zarina strove to share truths written in blood.

US_Torso01_P01.Description: A loose jacket to conceal the blood smeared equipment she carries.

US_Legs01_P01.Description: Flexible denim pants to venture Brooklyn and brave any type of… trouble.

US_Torso01_01.Description: A weathered leather jacket to conceal the clunky recording devices she carries for impromptu interviews.

K20_Body01.Description: Born from the unhinged minds of his victims tormented by guilt.

K20_Weapon01.Description: A massive chef's knife to reap affliction and misery from his victims.

S22_Legs01.Description: Fashionable skirt and warm boots to face what lurks in the dark.

K20_Body01_P01.Description: Born from the unhinged minds of his victims that he tormented with brutal and sanguinary methods.

K20_W01_P01.Description: A massive, bloodstained chef's knife to reap affliction and misery from his victims.

S22_Head01_P01.Description: Caring and impulsive, Cheryl Mason, previously known as Heather, attempted to rebuild her life after the tragic death of her adoptive father, Harry Mason… whose blood, she felt, was on her hands.

S22_Torso01_P01.Description: A cozy, weathered, bloodstained vest that keep her from harm at night.

S22_Legs01_P01.Description: Fashionable skirt drenched in blood and warm boots to face what lurks in the dark.

S23_Torso01.Description: A pricey suit jacket that remains durable through the most stressful presentations and arduous trials.

S23_Legs01.Description: Custom-tailored pants that provide more flexibility than expected.

S23_Head01_P01.Description: A talented and resolute architect, bloody from the endless trials.

S23_Torso01_P01.Description: Once a pricey suit jacket, it has the stains of suffering that can never be removed.

S23_Torso01_01.Description: An exceptional jacket and vest combo, worn during Felix’s reception of the German National Design Award.

AU_001.Description: No matter the design, we couldn’t make this as horrifying as 2020.

AU_002.Description: An assortment of blood-stained weaponry for all the vicious boys and girls.

AU_004.Description: It’s packed with all kinds of useful items and the Broken Key.

AU_005.Description: The fact that this ornament hasn’t been slashed, bludgeoned, or vomited on is a holiday miracle.

BI_001.Description: The foundation of a mysterious tower.

BI_002.Description: A half-built tower that holds secrets in its cold walls.

BI_003.Description: An enigmatic tower that stands out from the barren landscape.

BI_004.Description: A tower bursting with unharnessed possibility.

BI_005.Description: A mock-up of a logo that a Sakura 7 gang member carved into a table.

BI_006.Description: A keychain from the forum Claudette moderated.

BI_007.Description:
It’s your wacky elephant pal as a plush toy! He can’t wait to play in your red puddles! 

Design inspired by kangyaku.

BI_009.Description: A rare flower that grows in Cuba and Florida. Claudette’s favorite.

BI_010.Description: The figure of a Japanese ogre. It’s smiling viciously.

BI_011.Description: Everything Sally held dear was taken away.

BI_012.Description: An artifact once prevalent in The Entity’s realm, it vanished quite suddenly.

BI_013.Description: A treat made by pouring hot maple sap onto snow. Part of French-Canadian culture, where it’s known as tire d'érable.

BI_014.Description: The hand of someone who succumbed to the cold night.

BI_015.Description: An oxymoron known as frozen hot cocoa.

BI_016.Description: A relic from the Observer’s tower. Some say these roses once held powerful sway over The Entity’s realm.

BI_017.Description: A flag marking the end of a race, its significance is diminished in a realm where endings are ambiguous.

BI_018.Description: A knife-shaped icicle. May be effective at killing snowmen.

BI_019.Description: A tattoo Kazan stripped from a man’s skin, deeming him unworthy of wearing such a noble symbol.

BI_020.Description: A relic from the halls of Crotus Prenn Asylum.

BI_021.Description: It may have been beautiful once, but such things are the first to break in this realm.

BI_022.Description: A souped-up streetbike that Yui rode to many victories on.

BI_023.Description: Sally’s wedding ring. Only a piece of that woman remained.

BI_024.Description: She doubted the work she performed but had little else remaining.

BI_025.Description: The death of her husband tore her soul apart.

BI_026.Description: She was drifting towards a monstrous act as she succumbed to the darkness.

BI_027.Description: She understood her purpose now. And it was to cleanse.

BI_028.Description: The dream felt real. And in it, she was utterly destroyed.

BI_029.Description: She felt empty after witnessing the horrible crash of her friend.

BI_030.Description: There was a thought she couldn’t purge from her mind: Revenge.

BI_031.Description: What does it matter if you gain the world if you lose your humanity?

BI_032.Description: She realized some things are more important than first place.

BI_033.Description: A strong and reliable beast with an indomitable will.

BI_034.Description: A beacon of hope in a realm of suffering and despair.

DR_001.Description: An old, disheveled room that reeks of despair.

DR_002.Description: A squalid home, but far better than the rest of The Entity's Realm.

DR_003.Description: A reprieve from the nearby horrors.

DR_004.Description: Warm and peaceful, the only danger being the tedium of isolation.

DR_005.Description: Maybe it's best to lay low and wait for all of this to blow over.

DR_006.Description: Proof that zombies can't pilot helicopters.

DR_007.Description: The favorite location of your teammate.

DR_008.Description: Being brave doesn't mean you're not scared. It means you're scared as hell, and then you pick up the shotgun anyway.

DR_009.Description: A design that Bill remembers from back before his hair greyed.

DR_010.Description: An ancient artifact from a religion that worshipped Assyrian, Sumerian, and Babylonian gods.

DR_011.Description: A golden figure of the sea goat, said to be the God of Water and Creation.

DR_012.Description: Somehow it feels more important than just any mangled zombie hand.

DR_013.Description: A digital camera that's never far from Zarina.

DR_014.Description: An ancient coin purchased by the wealthy to prove their devotion.

DR_015.Description: Don't let it fool you, leaving is never that easy.

DR_016.Description: What's this guy doing in The Entity's realm?

DR_017.Description: The Z in her name seemed beyond the comprehension of many, and Zarina found that she was often Karina.

DR_018.Description: A ceremonial dagger used to slice the tongue from a blasphemer.

DR_019.Description: An ancient tablet that depicts the High Priestess of Babylon purifying the masses.

DR_020.Description: A zombie nearly bursting with bile. Reminiscent of the time Mom undercooked the thanksgiving turkey.

DR_021.Description: An ominous sign, dripping in blood...

DR_022.Description: The first trophy Zarina won for her documentary work.

DR_023.Description: She took the words as truth and, as much as it pained her, accepted the necessity of spilt blood.

DR_024.Description: She did not understand how her mentor could question the gods.

DR_025.Description: She lied to the Maiden Guard to protect the man who raised her.

DR_026.Description: She begged the gods for an answer, and it arrived as a whisper, angry and thirsting for blood.

DR_027.Description: She allowed the whisper to influence her, no matter how difficult it pained her.

DR_028.Description: The world was snafued, and he was in the middle of it.

DR_029.Description: He found other survivors, even though one of them was a loudmouthed blowhard.

DR_030.Description: He fought alongside the others, freeing a young man from a perilous situation.

DR_031.Description: He was a value to his squad and he knew how to keep them in line.

DR_032.Description: He was ready, able to act on instinct. A part of himself even missed this feeling.

DR_034.Description: An unlucky crow, stripped to its bones in the Observer's tower.

EC_001.Description: The rusted logo of the biomedical multinational Umbrella Corporation.

EC_002.Description: A crusted fragment of blood that holds great importance in the realm.

EC_003.Description:
It would be dangerous not to invite this bear to the party.
"Thank you for keeping the party going for five years. You’ll always be on the invite list!" —The Dead by Daylight Team

EC_004.Description:
A candle for every year in The Entity’s realm.
"Let’s keep the fire burning and the blood flowing! Cheers!" —The Dead by Daylight Team

EC_005.Description: An engraved skull with hollowed eyes, an omen of death.

EC_006.Description: An orb made of toothed cogwheels, each meshing with the other to power up a dark energy.

FL_001.Description: Thick layers of rot and decay make it impossible to distinguish what’s within.

FL_002.Description: This was more than rotting pages. This was an invitation to a universe of tales.

FL_003.Description: There was something real within the pages, as if they told a truth of some kind.

FL_004.Description: The stories were terrifying, but they held answers to mysteries within the horror.

FL_005.Description: A casualty of Jake Park’s rugged survivalist lifestyle.

FL_006.Description: A pleasant image, but once a wave hits all the sand people inside will surely die.

FL_007.Description: A tick bloated on the blood of Jake Park.

FL_008.Description: A calm spirit can only go so far when you’ve got dinner to protect.

FL_009.Description: The compass had acted strangely, as if leading Jake into the fog.

FL_010.Description: A bucket of deep-fried fingers, straight from the carnival’s deep fryers.

FL_011.Description: The circus was full of tricks no sane individual could foresee.

FL_012.Description: An image so fresh and tantalizing that it’s starkly out of place in this realm.

FL_013.Description: A stone carving that looked on as Élodie explored the streets below.

FL_014.Description: An all-time classic that’s one of Jeffrey Hawk’s most valued possessions.

FL_015.Description: A simple comfort from a memory long ago...

FL_016.Description: An intensely disturbing floatation device that may be more interested in drowning you.

FL_017.Description: An urban landscape littered with marks and arrows to explore.

FL_018.Description: An early design of The Huntress’ mask, carved into scratched and chipped wood.

FL_019.Description: A grim collection of human fingers and animal parts.

FL_020.Description: Within the larger figure is a young child, clinging to her doll.

FL_021.Description: A phenomenon of The Entity’s realm, mysterious and pulsing with blood.

FL_022.Description: Though broken, the musical instrument served as a memento to Élodie following her parent’s disappearance.

FL_023.Description: He was angry at the world... and a raccoon too.

FL_024.Description: He saw what could only be described as a treasure.

FL_025.Description: Much of the thrill came from the hunt itself.

FL_026.Description: He knew what he wanted, and no amount of talk could change his mind.

FL_027.Description: It’s true... the best jokes are when someone gets hurt.

FL_028.Description: Having escaped to nature, he was free from the pressures of society.

FL_029.Description: He knew there would be challenges. Primal challenges.

FL_030.Description: To live, something else must die.
